I deactivated my account this week and would encourage everyone else to do the same.  I received a notification from the app that I had been added to  a credit account and to open the app for more details.  The notification used a string of initials for the lending institution making it impossible to identify the account.  On opening the app there was no information anywhere about a new account or an addition to an open credit account.  I immediately contacted their support and after four days and three contact attempts (ticket number 9262902) I still have not received anything from them.  For a service that claims to "make the most of your credit" they only seem interested in pitching you credit card offers and mortgage refinancing, and no care whatsoever for potential fraud or the accuracy of their service.
